item.description:
Join me at this venue that should be familiar to many of you from dancing meetups.
Either come to sing or to watch others (including me) sing.
You don't have to solo; two or more people can sing together.
Karaoke starts at 8:30.
There are some pretty good regulars who come to sing here, including an excellent Elvis.
You can order food and/or drinks.
You can also dance to the karaoke songs.
I am listing this event with other meetup groups.
item.how_to_find_us: Either I'll have a meetup sign or wear my "NEIL" hat
